description "Rebel Sapper 

2-life electronic saboteurs with damage-boosted gadgets.

^2Weaponry:
- Light Melee
-- Tracks on hit
-- 20% faster RoF
- DL-44 Blaster Pistol (2)
-- 20% less Dmg
- E-11 Blaster Carbine (CR-2 2)
-- 10% more Velocity
-- 15% less Dmg
- Pulse Grenade Launcher (M5)
-- 65% faster RoF
-- Sec only
- Pulse Grenades (2)
- Det Packs (2)
-- Pushes on det
-- 40% faster RoF
- Tracking Trip Mines (2)
-- Tracks on hit
-- 50% less Dmg

^5Powers:
- Magna-Glove (Pull 1)
- Wrist Shocker (Lightning 1) ^3[CS4]

^6Inventory:
- Seeker Drone ^3[CS1]
- Stimpak ^3[CS3]

^8Attributes:
- Reinforcement (1)
- 15% faster Hacking
- 10% more Kb Taken
- 200% slower Skill Cd
- Resource Regen: 5/s
- Dexterity (1)
- Armor Regen: 2/s to 20
- Tracking Beacon
- Assemble (2)

^3Abilities:
- Gunkick ^3[CS2]"